data.description: Welcome to the serene community of Mira Lago, a haven away from the hustle and bustle of Tampa city life, yet conveniently close to all the vibrant amenities of the Tampa Bay area. Come see this 4 bedroom 2 bath home in a gated community for your security. Step into this well maintained and freshly painted home, where the open living space welcomes you with luxurious vinyl plank flooring extending seamlessly from the living room to the dining room, family room, and master bedroom. The master bedroom has a walk in closet. The three additional bedrooms boast well-preserved carpeting in excellent condition, providing a cozy retreat for all family members.   The spacious kitchen is designed for family enjoyment, creating a central hub for shared cooking experiences. Both the kitchen and bathrooms feature tasteful ceramic tile flooring, combining style with easy maintenance.  Relax on the lanai and take in the beauty of the backyard oasis. Step into your private outdoor space, set up chairs, and enjoy the peaceful lake view to your left. Mira Lago is a highly sought-after gated community, ensures your security and offers desirable amenities, including a pool and playground for families to delight in.  Remarkably, the HOA and CDD fees are notably low compared to others in the area, making this home an excellent investment in a secure and thriving community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Mira Lago residence your own – come and see for yourself!
